            "mimeType": "text/css",
            "text": "\n/* CoolMenus 4 - default styles - do not edit */\n.clCMAbs\n{\n\tposition: absolute; \n\tvisibility: hidden; \n\tdisplay: none; \n\tleft: 0; \n\ttop: 0;\n}\n/* CoolMenus 4 - default styles - end */\n  \n/*Style for the background-bar*/\n.clBar\n{\n\tposition:absolute; \n\twidth:10; \n\theight:10; \n\tbackground-color:333333; \n\t/*layer-background-color:333333; */\n\tvisibility:hidden;\n\n}\n\n/*Styles for level 0*/\n.clLevel0,.clLevel0over\n{\n\tposition: absolute; \n\tfont-family: arial, verdana, lucida, helvetica, sans-serif; \n\tfont-size: 12px; \n\ttext-align: center;\n}\n\n.clLevel0\n{\n\tbackground-color: #546c76;\n\t/*layer-background-color: #546c76;*/\n\tcolor: #FFFFFF;\n\tborder-top: 1px solid #FFFFFF;\n}\n\n.clLevel0over\n{\n\tbackground-color:#3c505b; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#3c505b;\t*/\n\tcolor: #DDDDDD; \n\tcursor: pointer; \n\t/*cursor: hand;*/\n\tborder-top: 2px solid #AAAAAA;\n}\n\n.clLevel0border\n{\t\n\tposition:absolute; \n\tvisibility:hidden; \n\tbackground-color:#000000; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#000000;*/\n}\n\n/*Styles for level 1*/\n.clLevel1, .clLevel1over\n{\n\tposition:absolute; \n\tpadding:2px; \n\tfont-family: arial, verdana, lucida, helvetica, sans-serif;\n\tfont-size:12px; \n}\n\n.clLevel1\n{\n\tbackground-color:#D9DCE5; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#D9DCE5; */\n\tcolor:#000000;\n}\n\n.clLevel1over\n{\n\tbackground-color:#3c505b; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#3c505b; */\n\tcolor:#FFFFFF; \n\tcursor:pointer; \n\t/*cursor:hand; */\n}\n\n.clLevel1border\n{\n\tposition:absolute; \n\tvisibility:hidden; \n\tbackground-color:#B2B1BF; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#B2B1BF;*/\n}\n\n/*Styles for level 2*/\n.clLevel2, .clLevel2over\n{\n\tposition:absolute; \n\tpadding-top:2px; \n\tfont-size:12px;\n\tfont-family: arial, verdana, lucida, helvetica, sans-serif;\n}\n\n.clLevel2\n{\n\tbackground-color:#D9DCE5; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#D9DCE5; */\n\tcolor:#000000;\n}\n\n.clLevel2over\n{\n\tbackground-color:#3c505b; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#3c505b; */\n\tcolor:#FFFFFF; \n\tcursor:pointer; \n\t/*cursor:hand; */\n}\n\n.clLevel2border\n{\n\tposition:absolute; \n\tvisibility:hidden; \n\tbackground-color:#B2B1BF; \n\t/*layer-background-color:#B2B1BF;*/\n}\nA.menu_susp_root:link,A.menu_susp_root:visited,A.menu_susp_root:active,A.menu_susp_root:hover\n{\n\tcolor: #FFFFFF;\n\ttext-decoration: none;\n}\n"
